<!-- FAQ -->
<section class="section" style="padding-top: 24px;">
  <div class="section-header">
    <h2>Common Questions</h2>
  </div>
  <div class="faq-list">

    <details class="faq-item">
      <summary class="faq-question">How long until my order is ready?</summary>
      <div class="faq-answer">
        <p>Most orders are printed and ready within <strong>1–3 days</strong>. During busy periods this may take a little longer. We'll message you as soon as it's ready to collect.</p>
      </div>
    </details>

    <details class="faq-item">
      <summary class="faq-question">How will I get my order?</summary>
      <div class="faq-answer">
        <p>We operate on a <strong>collection-only</strong> basis. Once your order is ready, we'll be in touch to arrange a convenient time and place to meet up in Edinburgh.</p>
      </div>
    </details>

    <details class="faq-item">
      <summary class="faq-question">How do I pay?</summary>
      <div class="faq-answer">
        <p>We accept <strong>cash or card</strong> on collection. If you paid by card online through the website, you're already sorted — no need to pay again.</p>
      </div>
    </details>

    <details class="faq-item">
      <summary class="faq-question">I haven't heard anything yet — should I be worried?</summary>
      <div class="faq-answer">
        <p>Not at all! If you've just placed your order, we'll be in touch once it's printed and ready. If it's been more than a few days and you haven't heard from us, feel free to <a href="https://wa.me/message/LOBEWRYKAT5UI1" target="_blank">message us on WhatsApp</a> or <a href="mailto:christo3dprints@gmail.com">send us an email</a> and we'll update you straight away.</p>
      </div>
    </details>

    <details class="faq-item">
      <summary class="faq-question">Can I change or cancel my order?</summary>
      <div class="faq-answer">
        <p>If your order hasn't started printing yet, we can usually make changes. <a href="https://wa.me/message/LOBEWRYKAT5UI1" target="_blank">Message us on WhatsApp</a> as soon as possible and we'll do our best to help.</p>
      </div>
    </details>

    <details class="faq-item">
      <summary class="faq-question">Can I change the colour I chose?</summary>
      <div class="faq-answer">
        <p>If your order hasn't started printing yet, yes — just <a href="https://wa.me/message/LOBEWRYKAT5UI1" target="_blank">message us on WhatsApp</a> with your new colour choice and we'll update it for you.</p>
      </div>
    </details>

    <details class="faq-item">
      <summary class="faq-question">Do you deliver?</summary>
      <div class="faq-answer">
        <p>We're currently <strong>collection only</strong> in Edinburgh. We don't offer postal delivery at this time.</p>
      </div>
    </details>

    <details class="faq-item">
      <summary class="faq-question">Something is wrong with my order — what do I do?</summary>
      <div class="faq-answer">
        <p>We're sorry to hear that! Please <a href="https://wa.me/message/LOBEWRYKAT5UI1" target="_blank">message us on WhatsApp</a> or <a href="mailto:christo3dprints@gmail.com">email us</a> with a photo and description of the issue and we'll sort it out for you.</p>
      </div>
    </details>

  </div>
</section>

<!-- Still need help? -->
<section class="section" style="padding-top: 0;">
  <div class="cta-banner">
    <h2>Still need help?</h2>
    <p>We're always happy to answer questions — just reach out.</p>
    <a href="/contact/" class="btn btn-primary">Contact Us &#8594;</a>
  </div>
</section>
